com.avanza.astrix.provider.core

Annotation Type DefaultBeanSettings


  • @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
public @interface DefaultBeanSettings
    Allows Overriding the default bean settings for a given Astrix bean by annotating the exported bean type.

    Example usage 1, in service-interface definition: 

      @DefaultBeanSettings(initialTimeout = 2000)
 public interface TradingService {
    // Method definitions
 }
    Example usage 2, in Astrix bean definition: 
     
  @DefaultBeanSettings(initialTimeout = 3000)
  @Service
 public AccountService accountService();
    Author:
    Elias Lindholm (elilin)
